    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可容纳万人的开放世界, 每座城市可同时容纳 1 万人登入互动</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261390/extras/13eeddc4f3f3dc9f75c75b2aeefa61ae.avif?t=1757084354\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有商城, 没有储值点数, 所有的交易货币与装备皆在游戏中获得. 真正属于玩家的虚拟世界.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富的生存技能, 制作工艺. 让玩家在末日中建造自己的家园</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261390/extras/727e92a15c42a434859c536b2a75dec4.avif?t=1757084354\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从搏击剑道到忍术, 从裁缝铁匠到工艺大师, 从耕种采集到料理专家.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高达 200 种的生存技能自由搭配组合. 让每个角色都是独一而二的存在.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>真正将虚拟角色生殖器官与性互动机能还给玩家的原宇宙 </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261390/extras/970694b58e69472f7d95afffbf44b6e6.avif?t=1757084354\" width=600 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家与玩家之间可以进行各种性爱互动. 不需要额外安装Mod, 更不需要付费解锁.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>画面可同时呈现 2000只僵尸与玩家的战斗. 带来真正充满千百僵尸, 刺激艰苦的末日世界  </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261390/extras/3e754b0a0e80573964bbb860aaafcab6.avif?t=1757084354\" width=600 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >且所有战斗与移动相关运算皆在伺服器端进行, 没有外挂运作的空间.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>死亡不是结束, 扮演僵尸继续为逝去的生命而奋斗. 进化为新世界主宰 </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261390/extras/ba8289ded67bce850f17778be1822abf.avif?t=1757084354\" width=600 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家角色死亡后将可能被转换为僵尸角色, 虽然无法跟装备精良的人类一搏, 但可指挥其他僵尸利用数量上的优势突袭. 成长后甚至可进化成新主宰物种.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>支援完整模组 - 在末日世界中收集并欣赏各种海报. 聆听音乐CD. 收集可爱公仔吊饰装饰角色 </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261390/extras/772d6b2ec6793f5bc139f38c3ca5c57e.avif?t=1757084354\" width=600 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 而这些收集道具都可以用 Mod 模组来换置成玩家希望的内容.</p>",
